daddy.

29
00:01:31.961 --> 00:01:33.495
We love you. daddy.

30
00:01:33.596 --> 00:01:35.797
Oh.
I love you both more.

31
00:01:35.898 --> 00:01:39.067
Let's see.
Let me see what we got here.

32
