Well. it's easy. mama.

75
00:04:23.299 --> 00:04:24.733
I love him. and he'll be fine
once he gets another job.

76
00:04:24.834 --> 00:04:26.067
You know.
everybody keeps saying

77
00:04:26.168 --> 00:04:28.203
