is about to rebound.

78
00:04:28.304 --> 00:04:29.838
No one I know
is saying that.

79
00:04:29.939 --> 00:04:32.140
They're all saying
it's gonna get even worse.

80
00:04:32.241 --> 00:04:33.641
Mama. that is
really not helpful.

81
00:04:33.743 --> 00:04:35.377
Do we have to talk about this
