127
00:06:19.949 --> 00:06:22.350
Be kind of a kick.
us working together again.

128
00:06:22.451 --> 00:06:26.521
All right. honey.
Take care.

129
00:06:35.297 --> 00:06:38.133
Um...

130
00:06:40.002 --> 00:06:41.336
Thanks.
Sorry.

131
00:07:01.857 --> 00:07:03.491
Come on.

132
00:07:32.821 --> 00:07:36.224
Wow. Not at all what
it looks like from the outside.

133
00:07:36.325 --> 00:07:38.059
Most things aren't.
hon.

134
00:07:38.160 --> 00:07:39.360
I like to put my money
where it matters.

135
00:07:39.461 --> 00:07:42.297
Georgia Cummings.
How can I help you?

136
00:07:42.398 --> 00:07:44.766
Riley Parks. We spoke
on the phone about the job.

137
00:07:44.867 --> 00:07:47.669
Oh. right.
Selena's friend.

138
00:07:47.770 --> 00:07:50.104
Well.
aren't you a lovely thing.

139
00:07:50.206 --> 00:07:51.839
Oh. thank you.

140
00:07:51.941 --> 00:07:53.541
Um. I specialize
in deep-tissue and reflexology.

141
00:07:53.642 --> 00:07:55.877
and this is my résumé
with references. of course.

142
00:07:55.978 --> 00:07:58.880
References.
Well. very thorough.

143
00:07:58.981 --> 00:07:59.981
Thank you.

144
00:08:00.082 --> 00:08:01.916
Well.
here's the deal. honey.

145
00:08:02.017 --> 00:08:04.352
