fat yes about you.

147
00:08:09.124 --> 00:08:10.658
So. when would you
like to start?

148
00:08:10.759 --> 00:08:13.127
Well. that's it?
I'm hired?

149
00:08:13.229 --> 00:08:15.279
Well. I could give you a
typing test if you would like...

150
00:08:15.731 --> 00:08:17.632
...but I don't think
that would apply.

151
00:08:17.733 --> 00:08:21.035
No. no. It's fine.
It's fantastic. Wow.

152
00:08:21.136 --> 00:08:23.204
I know.
It's tough out there. right?

153
00:08:23.305 --> 00:08:26.708
Tough to get a job.
and tough to hold on to it.

154
00:08:26.809 --> 00:08:29.711
Very.
And I am very grateful.

155
00:08:29.812 --> 00:08:31.512
Just one thing.

156
00:08:31.614 --> 00:08:33.581
Okay.
Here come the buts.

157
00:08:33.682 --> 00:08:35.850
Two things. actually.

158
00:08:35.951 --> 00:08:36.918
My kids.

159
00:08:37.019 --> 00:08:39.187
Um. I need my hours
to be flexible.

160
00:08:39.288 --> 00:08:42.457
Don't worry. honey. This job
is all about flexibility.

161
00:08:42.558 --> 00:08:45.827
Let me show you around.

162
00:08:57.973 --> 00:09:00.308
Hey.
I got the job.

163
00:09:00.409 --> 00:09:02.076
And Dairy Queen
to celebrate.

164
00:09:02.177 --> 00:09:03.945
Baby. that's great.
Yeah. the owner of the place said

165
00:09:04.046 --> 00:09:05.847
that I had exactly
what she was looking for.

166
00:09:05.948 --> 00:09:07.649
and she uses her eyes
and her guts and --

167
00:09:07.750 --> 00:09:09.050
I don't know.
Isn't that the best news?

168
00:09:09.151 --> 00:09:10.084
You hear that. kids?

169
00:09:10.185 --> 00:09:11.953
Mommy is the official
new breadwinner.

170
00:09:13.422 --> 00:09:15.923
That's great. mommy.
Thanks.

171
00:09:16.025 --> 00:09:18.326
You okay?
Yeah.

172
00:09:19.762 --> 00:09:22.163
I'm real proud of you.

173
00:09:25.434 --> 00:09:28.169
Okay.
What flavor do y'all want?

174
00:09:28.270 --> 00:09:29.337
Mint chocolate chip!

175
00:09:29.438 --> 00:09:31.239
Mint chocolate chip?
I happen to have that.

176
00:09:37.246 --> 00:09:39.747
Oh. hey. Riley.
You made it.

177
00:09:39.848 --> 00:09:41.349
I'm Dee Ann.
Oh.

178
00:09:41.450 --> 00:09:43.651
Wow. Quite a grip
you got there.

179
00:09:43.752 --> 00:09:44.986
That's why
I make the big bucks.

180
00:09:45.087 --> 00:09:47.188
Hi.
Hi.

181
00:09:47.289 --> 00:09:49.490
Oh. this is Jolene. or.
as I call her. no fun at all.

182
00:09:49.591 --> 00:09:50.758
Oh. I'm sure
that's not true.

183
00:09:50.859 --> 00:09:53.161
Well. it is true.
and I'm damn proud of it.

184
00:09:53.262 --> 00:09:55.196
and do not believe
everything she tells you.

185
00:09:55.297 --> 00:09:59.300
I have a client.
Hey. I'm Kendra.

186
00:09:59.401 --> 00:10:01.469
Oh. if really happy.
cheerful people make you sick.

187
00:10:01.570 --> 00:10:03.137
you'll want to stay away.

188
00:10:03.238 --> 00:10:04.806
Nice to meet you.
Riley.

189
00:10:04.907 --> 00:10:08.509
If there's ever anything
you need help with. just ask.

190
00:10:08.610 --> 00:10:10.111
Thanks. I will.

191
00:10:10.212 --> 00:10:11.979
So. you excited
about your first day?

192
00:10:12.081 --> 00:10:14.048
Yeah. yeah. it's kind of like
that first day of school.

193
00:10:14.149 --> 00:10:15.650
