down the hallway.

195
00:10:17.052 --> 00:10:19.721
Actually. um.
he's coming in at 10:00.

196
00:10:25.928 --> 00:10:27.328
You ready?

197
00:10:27.429 --> 00:10:28.429
Sure. Come on in.

198
00:10:28.530 --> 00:10:31.099
Hi. Hank.
I'm Riley.

199
00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:32.600
So. you're here
for one hour?

200
00:10:32.701 --> 00:10:34.302
Having some issues
with your shoulder?

201
00:10:34.403 --> 00:10:35.970
Uh. yeah.

202
00:10:36.071 --> 00:10:38.873
Uh. my hips and legs
are a little tight. too.

203
00:10:38.974 --> 00:10:41.008
Oh. okay.
I can take care of that.

204
00:10:41.110 --> 00:10:47.281
So. any other issues or injuries
that I need to worry about?

205
00:10:47.383 --> 00:10:49.417
Uh. no. I'm good.
Okay.

206
00:10:50.919 --> 00:10:54.489
Wow. You're pretty.

207
00:10:54.590 --> 00:10:56.958
Oh.
You're cute. yourself.

208
00:11:01.130 --> 00:11:03.197
Uh...

209
00:11:03.298 --> 00:11:05.266
Hips and legs --
little tight.

210
00:11:05.367 --> 00:11:08.002
Oh. Yeah. Sure.

211
00:11:09.605 --> 00:11:10.905
That's better.

212
00:11:12.207 --> 00:11:13.441
Nice.

213
00:11:13.542 --> 00:11:15.510
Hank!

214
00:11:15.611 --> 00:11:16.944
Hank.
what are you doing?

215
00:11:17.045 --> 00:11:18.646
What do you mean?
Wh-- nothing.

216
00:11:18.747 --> 00:11:21.549
Well. good because
that's not on the menu.

217
00:11:21.650 --> 00:11:24.452
Lord.
Let me do my job.

218
00:11:24.553 --> 00:11:27.054
Here. Your hands obviously
need some attention.

219
00:11:27.156 --> 00:11:29.056
Uh. okay.

220
00:11:29.158 --> 00:11:31.492
This really isn't
what I had in mind.

221
00:11:31.593 --> 00:11:35.830
I don't want to be rude. but
the girls that don't give extras

222
00:11:35.931 --> 00:11:38.599
don't really do very well
here.

223
00:11:41.470 --> 00:11:43.671
I would like for you
to leave now.

224
00:11:43.772 --> 00:11:46.441
But I don't have
any clothes on.

225
00:11:50.667 --> 00:11:51.883
Oh. you're leaving early?

226
00:11:51.885 --> 00:11:53.686
You didn't think
it was important to tell me

227
00:11:53.787 --> 00:11:55.087
that the guys here
expect extras?

228
00:11:55.188 --> 00:11:56.422
