with two kids.

229
00:11:56.523 --> 00:11:58.157
That is not my idea
of a happy ending.

230
00:11:58.258 --> 00:12:00.526
Selena didn't explain it
to you?

231
00:12:00.627 --> 00:12:03.195
Girl. how'd you think
I was making so much money?

232
00:12:03.296 --> 00:12:05.331
If a guy needs a little something --
Selena.

233
00:12:05.432 --> 00:12:08.034
Adios. I got this.

234
00:12:09.736 --> 00:12:11.737
Riley.

235
00:12:15.042 --> 00:12:18.110
90% of what we do here
is legit.

236
00:12:18.211 --> 00:12:20.446
I have a client list
for a few guys

237
00:12:20.547 --> 00:12:22.448
who like
a little something extra.

238
00:12:22.549 --> 00:12:24.950
Selena had me believing that
was what you were looking for.

239
00:12:25.052 --> 00:12:28.287
If not. I have plenty of girls.
like Jolene.

240
00:12:28.388 --> 00:12:30.689
who only give
straight massages.

241
00:12:30.791 --> 00:12:35.127
Just to be clear.
I don't give extras.

242
00:12:35.228 --> 00:12:37.029
Mama?

243
00:12:37.130 --> 00:12:40.733
You and the kids back
from the movies?

244
00:12:43.103 --> 00:12:46.205
Kyle?

245
00:12:48.308 --> 00:12:50.543
[ Angus & Julia Stone's
"Hold On" plays ]

246
00:13:14.701 --> 00:13:19.705
♪ And I'm waiting for the day

247
00:13:24.411 --> 00:13:29.482
♪ what am I waiting for?

248
00:13:29.583 --> 00:13:36.422
♪ Hold on.
what did you say that for? ♪

249
00:13:36.523 --> 00:13:44.763
♪ hold on. what did
